<del rend="strikethrough"> beſunder / was </del> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Karl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r2l5"><expan>Holcʒſchüh<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd ſeins <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> manns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r2l6">vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchof <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough">was ſ</del> wenn ſie die ſchof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r2l7">vor vns <expan>behab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr ſeÿ / . vnd wir ew das </ab>
