</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_494" id="246v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und Hansen <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, den Wildensteinern czü Wildenfels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wildenstein<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        brief <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Karl <expan>Holczschüh<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und seins <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        manns und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> schof <expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> wenn sie die schof vor uns
                                <expan>behab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ir
                        sey, und wir ew das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so wöllet
                        ir die pürgen gern darumb ledig <expan>sage<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ew wissen, daz der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Karl
                            <expan>Holczschüh<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Rechperg<ex>er</ex></expan>, sein arm man,
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> schof vor uns czü den heiligen behabt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz die ir beder sein und daz sie das
                        den <expan>Goczman<ex>n</ex>en</expan> noch den iren nicht cze hilff noch ew
                            <expan>cze schade<ex>n</ex></expan> tün ungeverlichen,
                                <expan>awsgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> bey xxxvi schoffen, die
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglolffst<ex>ein</ex></expan> czü <expan>Vorch<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<add><expan>arme<ex>n</ex>manns</expan></add> sein, die sie in iren eiden
                        hindan gesaczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n.</expan></ab>
</div>
